title: China Central Television (CCTV): Online Music Lessons
description:
CCTV does a story about online music lessons from http://ArtistWorks.com 
featuring a student of fingerstyle guitarist Martin Taylor, classical guitarist Jason Vieaux, and ArtistWorks founder David Butler.

Just like Mike from nearby Oakland, you can learn from masters, Martin Taylor and Jason Vieaux. 

ArtistWorks Online Music Schools work like this:
1. Get a complete HD video library of  lessons, plus tabs, notation and more
Submit practice videos and get personalized Video Exchange™ feedback from the legendary instructors
2. Learn by watching the instructor's exchanges with other students
3. Get inspiration from a worldwide community of enthusiastic players working together with the instructor

The ArtistWorks Music Campus includes instructions in jazz, acoustic, electric guitars, electric bass, bluegrass instruments, and several classical instruments. All the schools are instructed by famous musicians from major symphonies, such as The Philadelphia Orchestra. 

An access to these teachers and to hundreds of HD lessons for only about a dollar a day. Your satisfaction is guaranteed. Find out more and join today!
fulltitle: China Central Television (CCTV): Online Music Lessons
